OL,3,CVaping banned at pub as landlord says
OL,4,C'it's just not right'
OL,6,FVaping has been banned in one of
OL,7,FKent's oldest pubs, as the landlord
OL,8,Fsays "it's just not right."
OL,10,FThe Three Horseshoes in Hernhill,
OL,11,Fbetween Faversham and Canterbury, has
OL,12,Fput up signs warning people against
OL,13,Fusing the devices inside.
OL,15,FMaurice O'Flynn says he is a heavy
OL,16,Fsmoker and was happy to enforce the
OL,17,Fsmoking ban which came into place in
OL,18,F2007 - but does not see why it is not
OL,19,Fthe same rule for vaping.
