OL,3,CVaping banned at pub as landlord says
OL,4,C'it's just not right'
OL,6,FHe said: "On a Sunday afternoon, we
OL,7,Fwere quite busy, I noticed that there
OL,8,Fwere some people sitting at the bar
OL,9,Fthat were vaping.
OL,11,F"It occurred to me that 'this isn't
OL,12,Fright.' It doesn't look right, it
OL,13,Fdoesn't smell right, it's just not
OL,14,Fright.
OL,16,F"I don't think it's courteous of
OL,17,Fanybody to start blowing smoke around
OL,18,Fthe place where there are people
OL,19,Feating.
