OL,3,CVaping banned at pub as landlord says
OL,4,C'it's just not right'
OL,6,F"I would certainly not want anybody,
OL,7,Fin close proximity, vaping while I was
OL,8,Ftrying to eat, and that's coming from
OL,9,Fa particularly heavy smoker."
OL,11,FThe ban on smoking in pubs, clubs,
OL,12,Frestaurants and various other venues
OL,13,Fcame into effect on 1 July 2007.
OL,15,FIn recent years, sales of electronic
OL,16,Fcigarettes and disposable vapes, have
OL,17,Fsoared in the UK with around 4.5
OL,18,Fmillion users.
